---
title: Brie, Caramelized Onion and Bacon Sandwiches with Apple Arugula Salad and Fig Vinaigrette
description: Fig jam and caramelized onions come together with ooey-gooey melted brie in this irresistible sandwich. The sweet richness is balanced by a zesty apple and arugula salad on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-au-brie-aux-oignons-caramelises-et-au-bacon-0df05e2c.jpg
